      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\nThe SUSE Linux Enterprise Micro 6.0 and Micro 6.1 kernel was updated to fix one security issue\n\nThe following security issue was fixed:\n\n- CVE-2026-31431: The copy.fail security issue is fixed by revert to operating out-of-place in algif_aead (bsc#1262573).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
